== Text Pointer Format ==

=== Pointer Table Structure ===

<pre>
Base: $e0:0000
Each pointer: 2 bytes (bank-relative offset)
Total pointers: Variable per bank

Example:
$e0:0000 = $8000  (Dialog 0 at $e0:8000)
$e0:0002 = $8045  (Dialog 1 at $e0:8045)
$e0:0004 = $80a2  (Dialog 2 at $e0:80A2)
...
</pre>

