== Dialog Extraction ==

To extract all dialog:

<pre>
1. Dump banks $e0-$e7
2. Parse pointer tables at bank start
3. Decode text using TBL
4. Handle control codes ($f0-$ff)
5. Export to JSON/CSV
</pre>

